    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hell Shooter</strong>是一款Roguelike地牢探索游戏。独特的攻击方式、惊险刺激的动作、东方地狱的氛围以及每个角色的故事讲述。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >独特的攻击方式</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181290/extras/2eb5d15d29ce89807a39ff7d5163bd15.poster.avif?t=1756972850\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181290/extras/2eb5d15d29ce89807a39ff7d5163bd15.webm?t=1756972850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181290/extras/2eb5d15d29ce89807a39ff7d5163bd15.mp4?t=1756972850\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >攻击敌人时，必须冲锋才能杀死敌人！！在建筑物和敌人之间弹跳以设计最佳攻击路径。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >灵魂爆发</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181290/extras/96190dee2a2cf793494375854d8ddde2.poster.avif?t=1756972850\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181290/extras/96190dee2a2cf793494375854d8ddde2.webm?t=1756972850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181290/extras/96190dee2a2cf793494375854d8ddde2.mp4?t=1756972850\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >出色的发挥会得到奖励。收集组合量表并释放你的灵魂。这将是一次强有力的射击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >100 件</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181290/extras/2776a094ce0339303de01981cce9f606.poster.avif?t=1756972850\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181290/extras/2776a094ce0339303de01981cce9f606.webm?t=1756972850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181290/extras/2776a094ce0339303de01981cce9f606.mp4?t=1756972850\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无数的物品将帮助你的冒险。收集更多物品并施展强力攻击</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >阴间的鬼魂</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181290/extras/97ce8c92c7e21c8ce5c10e751794e0df.avif?t=1756972850\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181290/extras_big/97ce8c92c7e21c8ce5c10e751794e0df.avif?t=1756972850 width=800 height=332 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用他们自己的故事面对鬼魂。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >考虑重复玩的游戏设计</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181290/extras/6d8c6bb9212dec4d91b050e63b46e1b0.poster.avif?t=1756972850\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181290/extras/6d8c6bb9212dec4d91b050e63b46e1b0.webm?t=1756972850\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181290/extras/6d8c6bb9212dec4d91b050e63b46e1b0.mp4?t=1756972850\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验每次探索都会发生变化的地下世界。死亡并不是结束。用你赚到的钱探索并购买援军和物品！</p>",
